  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large saucepan over medium heat",
    "Add the chopped onion, carrot, and celery and cook until the vegetables are tender",
    "Add the grated ginger and cook for 1 minute",
    "Stir in the curry powder and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the crushed canned tomatoes, coconut milk, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 20 minutes",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook for an additional 10 minutes",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed",
    "Serve the curry hot over rice or noodles"
